summary: Face presets I use to play and make screenshots.
descriptionHtml:
[b]Face presets I use to play and make screenshots. 
[size=6]Requirments
[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS Hairdos - HDT Physics[/url]
[/b]
I mostly used these textures: Demoniac, SG, True Daughters, Fair, Mature, Pride of Valhalla and others. 
Depending on the textures you may need to change Complexion slider.

I also included my CBBE body slide presets. Normal one I used 99% of the time. Extreme one was just made for fun.

More pictures you can find on my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/803131/?tb=images&pUp=1]Nexus profile[/url] or in [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/betsujin/albums/72157679314188573]this album[/url].
author: Betsujin
